  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST OUR UPCOMING GAME!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Your goal is to perfectly fit all the items into the inventory without leaving any empty space.<br>To do so, you have some features that can be useful:<br><br>Drag and Rotate:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/86f56c8e576fb6a531b17ca95f549aa5.poster.avif?t=1755925066\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/86f56c8e576fb6a531b17ca95f549aa5.webm?t=1755925066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/86f56c8e576fb6a531b17ca95f549aa5.mp4?t=1755925066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Assembling and disassembling items makes the game more versatile and challenging:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/31d2e8fe26e8d153a73806bcc2631ba3.poster.avif?t=1755925066\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/31d2e8fe26e8d153a73806bcc2631ba3.webm?t=1755925066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/31d2e8fe26e8d153a73806bcc2631ba3.mp4?t=1755925066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bags, Backpacks and Chests can be used as containers to make room to fit more items:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/a994de01aa96ab7897bc2ccfe87b2378.poster.avif?t=1755925066\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/a994de01aa96ab7897bc2ccfe87b2378.webm?t=1755925066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/a994de01aa96ab7897bc2ccfe87b2378.mp4?t=1755925066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than hand-drawn 100 items to organize and fit.<br></li><li>50 handcrafted levels.<br></li><li>Relaxing medieval music to make you feel the atmosphere.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Your goal is to perfectly fit all the items into the inventory without leaving any empty space.<br>To do so, you have some features that can be useful:<br><br>Drag and Rotate:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/86f56c8e576fb6a531b17ca95f549aa5.poster.avif?t=1755925066\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/86f56c8e576fb6a531b17ca95f549aa5.webm?t=1755925066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/86f56c8e576fb6a531b17ca95f549aa5.mp4?t=1755925066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Assembling and disassembling items makes the game more versatile and challenging:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/31d2e8fe26e8d153a73806bcc2631ba3.poster.avif?t=1755925066\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/31d2e8fe26e8d153a73806bcc2631ba3.webm?t=1755925066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/31d2e8fe26e8d153a73806bcc2631ba3.mp4?t=1755925066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bags, Backpacks and Chests can be used as containers to make room to fit more items:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/a994de01aa96ab7897bc2ccfe87b2378.poster.avif?t=1755925066\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183940/extras/a994de01aa96ab7897bc2